{"name": "Sussex Help Center", "alternate_name": "", "description": " Everyone in need is welcome.
We provide our community Sussex, Wantage and Montague the following at least Four Times a Week:

    Bags of food are given to your neighbors in need.
    Currently close to 75 to 100 households are served.
    Some people in these households are unemployed
    Often there is not enough income
    Some have physical or mental disabilities
    There are home-bound seniors
    Quite a few are single-parent households
    Some 75 local children benefit from our food distribution programs
